### Add points to task

PUT {{base_url}}/api/{{id}}/add/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "points": 5
}

### Add points to task - 404 user data not found

PUT {{base_url}}/api/test/add/100
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "points": 5
}

### Add points to task - 404 task data not found

PUT {{base_url}}/api/eva/add/100
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "points": 5
}


